<p class="my-4">Notification Component using vcerb syntax below:</p>

<Notification title="my title">
  Hello, world
</Notification>

<p class="my-4">Notification Component using <var>render</var> below:</p>

<%= render(NotificationComponent.new(title: "my title")) do %>
  Hello, World!
<% end %>

<p class="my-4">End of demo</p>
